&lt;li class=&#34;quiz false&#34;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Develop risk management is: the process of developing a document that formally authorizes the existence of a project and provides the project manager with the authority to apply organization resources to project activities.”&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The definition is for Develop project charter&lt;br /&gt;
 制定项目章程是制定文档的过程，该文档正式授权项目的存在并为项目经理提供将组织资源应用于项目活动的权限。”&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
