&lt;p&gt;If you are a small company, with only 1 project to consider, and the NPV of that project is +10,000.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&#34;options&#34;&gt;
&lt;li class=&#34;correct&#34;&gt;do the project&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;don’t do the project&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
