&lt;h2 id=&#34;java-database-connectivity-jdbc&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#java-database-connectivity-jdbc&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Java Database Connectivity (JDBC)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Create a &lt;strong&gt;Java Project&lt;/strong&gt; and name it  &lt;code&gt;CoffeeConnect&lt;/code&gt; .&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Download the jar file accompanying this exercise from Blackboard. mysql-connector-java-8.0.22.zip&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Create a folder in your project folder called  &lt;code&gt;libs&lt;/code&gt; .&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Copy the jar file into your  &lt;code&gt;libs&lt;/code&gt;  folder.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Right click on your project folder and choose &lt;strong&gt;Build Path &amp;gt; Configure Build Path…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
