&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Click on &lt;strong&gt;Libraries&lt;/strong&gt; tab then &lt;strong&gt;Modulepath&lt;/strong&gt;, then the &lt;strong&gt;Add JARs…&lt;/strong&gt; button&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://i.loli.net/2020/11/15/RowN8nYpzPqcKmh.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At the pop up expand your  &lt;code&gt;Coffee_Connect&lt;/code&gt;  folder and expand your  &lt;code&gt;libs&lt;/code&gt;  folder. Choose your jar file and press OK.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://i.loli.net/2020/11/15/pVYqr3hwiLQFyd5.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Click Apply and Close to exit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Download the  &lt;code&gt;Dao&lt;/code&gt;  java file accompanying this exercise from Blackboard, and copy and paste the file into your  &lt;code&gt;src&lt;/code&gt;  folder. Do the same for the  &lt;code&gt;TableViewer&lt;/code&gt;  file as well.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
